&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;designing-a-collection-of-cables&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://arturgower.github.io/publication/industry/umbilical/&#34;&gt;Designing a collection of cables&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;How to design a collection of cables to be both robust and flexible? The answer is to use continuous optimisation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;alignright&#34;&gt;
